  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The proposed study is intended to examine the connection between two types of inhibition -
      cognitive and motor and the connection between motor inhibitory functions and a single bout
      of physical exercise in the context of age and physical fitness.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
